title: Kelly Rowland Interview and more
itunes:title: Kelly Rowland Interview and more
description:
Today on the show we had the chocolate goddess Kelly Rowland call in where she spoke about making new music, thirst trapping and quarantine life. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Tik Tok Covid pranksters and afterwards opened up the phone lines to see if our listeners would be a guinea pig to test out vaccines for the virus.
